<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.5">
<l>ventiṟal vāṇaṉ vēḷvi yiṭameyti yaṅkōr kuṟaḷāki meymmai yuṇara</l>
<l>centoḻil vēta nāviṉ muṉiyāki vaiya maṭimūṉṟi rantu peṟiṉum</l>
<l>mantira mītu pōki matiniṉṟi 	ṟaiñca malarōṉva ṇaṅka vaḷarcēr</l>
<l>antara mēḻi ṉūṭu celavuytta pāta matunammai yāḷu maracē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Appearing in the place of the sacrifice of the very powerful king,</l>
<l rend="indent">having become a dwarf there,</l>
<l>As a sage on whose tongue were the Vedas [propounding] correct action</l>
<l rend="indent">so [we] may know truth,</l>
<l>Although requesting and getting [only] three footsteps of land,</l>
<l rend="indent">going atop [Mount] Mandara, as the moon stayed and paid reverence,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the blossom[-born] one worshipped,</l>
<l>The foot which saved [us] when it went through the seven heavens,</l>
<l rend="indent">where it reached and grew, is the sovereign that rules us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
